    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Cutting wand that operates by punch-tip action, cutting by perforating paper rather than slicing it. Designed for use in children's arts and crafts; used as well by paper conservators for preparing hinges, inlays, and fills.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
